<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als etlich ewr rete yeczunden auf
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gelawbsbrif an uns
                                <expan>geworb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und wir in darauf
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, von <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir F. <expan>Tandorff<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>empfolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> cze <expan>red<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in
                            <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
<expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und das gnediklich aufnemen wöllet. Und wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb, dinst und gevallnüzz beweisen
                                <expan>möhte<ex>n,</ex></expan> des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>
                        wir willig und <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das allczit
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>divis<ex>ionis</ex></expan>
<expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>lo<ex>rum.</ex></expan>
